{
  "texts": [
    "This approach significantly improves the generalization ability of the vehicle detector compared to traditional data augmentation methods.Reference [64]presented an improved GAN-based algorithm for enhancing highway traffic images under complex weather conditions.",
    "They combined the attention mechanism with multiscale feature fusion in generator networks to effectively reduce noise while enhancing attention to high-frequency information in images.",
    "The improved Patch GAN in the discriminator employs a local discrimination strategy to distinguish the generated image from the real image.",
    "The iterative process between the generator and the discriminator achieves a Nash equilibrium that ensures the integrity and authenticity of the recovered image.Reference [65]introduced a detection algorithm called YOLO-SASE.",
    "This algorithm is based on the YOLOv5 detection framework and the Super-Resolution Generative Adversarial Network (SRGAN) network [57]."
  ]
}